HEADWORD: Serpent
<hw>Ser"pent</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To wind; to encircle.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Evelyn.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Serpentaria</ent>⟦br⟧
